FEATURED WINES
Your flight attendant will inform you of today's selections.
White wine
Lurton Vin de Pays d'Oc Chardonnay 1996
Santa Carolina Chardonnay Estate Reserva 1996
Red wine
Santa Carolina Maipo Valley Cabernet Sauvignon 1995
Rothschild Cabernet Sauvignon 1997
TO BEGIN
Jumbo crabmeat with cornbread and a tarragon vinaigrette
Garden fresh salad
Accompanied by oil and vinegar or Gorgonzola dressing
MAIN COURSE
Grilled filet mignon with chasseur sauce
Accompanied by potato casserole and sautéed mushrooms
Sautéed turkey cutlet with puttanesca sauce
Complemented by sautéed celery and jalapeño polenta
*Crispy chicken breast with an herbed cream sauce
Served with cheese grits cake and green and yellow squash
Farfalle pasta
Offered with seafood and pesto
DESSERT
Ice cream sundae
BEN&JERRY'S. Vanilla and Coffee ice cream
accompanied by hot fudge sauce, wafer and whipped cream
STARBUCKS. coffee will be available throughout the flight.
Crystal Geyser Natural Alpine Spring Water
PRIOR TO
ARRIVAL
cookies warm from the oven
*On November 26 and 27, United Airlines will replace this entree with
the following special holiday selection
created by Sheila Lukins, America's own chef.
Honey-ginger turkey served with maple cranberry sauce
Accompanied by Sheila's best cornbread stuffing,
candied sweet potato whip, home-style apples and aromatic carrots
